Class Summary
Class Description
Add
The Add class provides a method to get the current date and time minus a specified number of days.
Hour
The Hour class represents an hour with a number of passengers and a comment.
HourWithDates
The HourWithDates class extends the Hour class and adds a timeOfEditing field, which represents the date and time
ListSubwStation
The ListSubwStation class extends the SubwayStation class and adds a List of Hour objects.
ListSubwStream
This class extends the ListSubwStation class to represent a subway station with streaming data.
ListSubwStreamPermission
The ListSubwStreamPermission class implements the TypePermission interface
Program
The Program class provides utility methods for reading and writing
SubwayStation
Represents a subway station with a name, opening year, and hours of operation.
XMLSerializer
The XMLSerializer class provides methods for serializing and deserializing SubwayStation objects to and from XML format.
XStreamJSONSerializer
This class provides methods for serializing and deserializing ListSubwStream objects to and from JSON format.
XStreamJSONSerializerTest
This class provides unit tests for the XStreamJSONSerializer class.
